pokedexEntries.red: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.
pokedexEntries.blue: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Uses its alluring eyes to enrapture its foe. It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls the foe to sleep.
pokedexEntries.gold: If it inflates to sing a lullaby, it can perform longer and cause sure drowsiness in its audience.
pokedexEntries.silver: Looking into its cute, round eyes causes it to sing a relaxing melody, inducing its enemies to sleep.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It rolls its cute eyes as it sings a soothing lullaby. Its gentle song puts anyone who hears it to sleep.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Jigglypuff's vocal chords can freely adjust the wavelength of its voice. This Pokémon uses this ability to sing at precisely the right wavelength to make its foes most drowsy.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: When this Pokémon sings, it never pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, Jigglypuff cannot breathe, endangering its life.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Nothing can avoid falling asleep hearing a Jigglypuff's song. The sound waves of its singing voice match the brain waves of someone in a deep sleep.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It captivates foes with its huge, round eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing a soothing melody.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.
pokedexEntries.diamond: When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy.
pokedexEntries.pearl: When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy.
pokedexEntries.platinum: When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: If it inflates to sing a lullaby, it can perform longer and cause sure drowsiness in its audience.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Looking into its cute, round eyes causes it to sing a relaxing melody, inducing its enemies to sleep.
pokedexEntries.black: When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy.
pokedexEntries.white: When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy.
pokedexEntries.black2: Looking into its cute, round eyes makes it start singing a song so pleasant listeners can't help but fall asleep.
pokedexEntries.white2: Looking into its cute, round eyes makes it start singing a song so pleasant listeners can't help but fall asleep.
pokedexEntries.x: It captivates foes with its huge, round eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing a soothing melody.
pokedexEntries.y: If it inflates to sing a lullaby, it can perform longer and cause sure drowsiness in its audience.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Jigglypuff's vocal cords can freely adjust the wavelength of its voice. This Pokémon uses this ability to sing at precisely the right wavelength to make its foes most drowsy.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: When this Pokémon sings, it never pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, Jigglypuff cannot breathe, endangering its life.
pokedexEntries.sun: It hugely inflates its stomach and sings a mysterious melody. If you hear this melody, you'll become sleepy right away.
pokedexEntries.moon: Jigglypuff possess a vocal range that exceeds 12 octaves, but each individual's singing skill depends on its own effort.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: Recordings of Jigglypuff’s strange lullabies can be purchased from department stores. These CDs can be found near the bedding area.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: The songs they sing are totally different depending on the region they live in. Some even sound like they’re shouting!
